description:
I can now control firing with the controller! it took way more time than i was expecting to have something to feed balls into the flywheels. even now there's a lot of issues: one motor keeps stalling and the chute and solenoid aren't quite reliable. it also took a bunch of time getting the circuit rated for 10 amps which is roughly what the solenoid draws


day by day I'm getting closer to trying to switch to an air compressor. this thing is so loud and janky.
